{"tid":2253521,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"高登：「高登真係玩完」我決定撐空姐唔係空雞，睇住你班社會垃圾真嘔心","createTime":"2020-10-22T08:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T08:59:45.000Z","uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e721452c7871a6248ac8f8989e4971f00a6dca2","tid":2253521,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：「高登真係玩完」我決定撐空姐唔係空雞，睇住你班社會垃圾真嘔心<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7318072/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7318072%2Fpage%2F1&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=5076c194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7318072/page/1</a><br />\n<blockquote>我原本都有笑班空雞，笑佢地終於落得如此下場<br />\n想話佢地抵死啦，罷工靠民航處。工會自己玩篤灰。係抵死嘅<br />\n問返自己，其實佢地真係咁黑我憎？大家都係人啫，係咪？<br />\n空姐都係人，唔通會為咗社運放棄份工咩？咁當時玩篤灰就要收皮㗎啦<br />\n姐係香港嘅黃絲咪又係咁，個個得把口，攬炒攬炒~<br />\n幾時有見過班黃絲真係罷工？有事就即刻縮沙㗎啦<br />\n錢字行頭嘅香港人又點可能會為咗社運放棄任何野呀？<br />\n一係就班勇字行頭唔識人間險惡嘅後生仔，其他人咪同班空姐咪一鳩樣<br />\n晚晚上Facebook大叫好嬲，第朝繼續返工。所以話笑空姐嘅人不知所謂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相信呢度有班人睇完好高興"},{"pid":"60d40135599da75a0fd213a2840b27fde2cfb819","tid":2253521,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<br />\n又空姐"},{"pid":"275fcb725069d8b22243ef6a4e8229dd41f48842","tid":2253521,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60d40135599da75a0fd213a2840b27fde2cfb819","tid":2253521,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<br />\n又空姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:35:38.000Z","msg":"入去條link睇吓先啦"},{"pid":"1dc6bd1c71b169c1c6c42912950342d58b08c080","tid":2253521,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"275fcb725069d8b22243ef6a4e8229dd41f48842","tid":2253521,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60d40